      "options": {
        "content": "### Correlation workflow\n1. Find spikes in latency/error-rate panels.\n2. Open **Logs by Trace ID** and copy any trace id from a suspicious line.\n3. Click **View trace** link (derived field) to jump into Tempo.\n4. In Tempo, use **Traces to logs** to pivot back to Loki with the same trace context.",
